XML_CLASS_PROPERTTY

public static final java.lang.String XML_CLASS_PROPERTTY
Name of the system properties used to identifies the default XML Parser.
The value of the properties MUST BE the fully qualified class name of
XML Parser which CyberLink should use.

loadDefaultXMLParser

private static Parser loadDefaultXMLParser()
This method loads the default XML Parser using the following behavior: - First if present loads the parsers specified by the system property XML_CLASS_PROPERTTY
- Second by a fall-back technique, it tries to load the XMLParser from one
of the following classes: JaxpParser, kXML2Parser, XercesParser

Returns:
Parser which has been loaded successuflly or null otherwise
Since:
1.8.0
